{"tid":868053,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[board game狼人] 求解決 有朋友偷睇點應對好","createTime":"2018-10-19T07:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T02:31:37.000Z","uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"26881a10ce8db8499d86dd4e732214f2c16fcb67","tid":868053,"uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:25:56.000Z","msg":"本身隻game係好好玩 透過分析同理論 <br />\n仲有唔同既神職慢慢一步一步咁搵出狼人<br />\n當中仲可以睇到唔同朋友平時唔會展露性格既一面<br />\n<br />\n但係有其中1個朋友就係夜晚個時不斷偷睇知道哂d人咩身份<br />\n本身我都唔信 後尾完左自己圍威喂幾個朋友講返先覺得唔對路 <br />\n而且1個朋友係死左個時(夜晚)望到佢偷睇人地所以更肯定佢係每次都有偷睇<br />\n所以佢可以係完全無根據同理由下知道哂邊d身份<br />\n同埋每晚都依據佢既身份殺到啱既人 我簡單用3鋪黎做例子你地就會明<br />\n<br />\n第1鋪 佢係守衛<br />\n我同另外2個朋友係狼人 即係總共3個狼人<br />\n<br />\n第1晚 我地其中1個狼人朋友自刀呃解藥 而佢應該係睇到狼人自刀所以揀左守衛自己<br />\n最後成功呃到女巫解藥 <br />\n第2晚 我地殺其中1個平民 佢守衝到<br />\n第3日 有預言家跳出黎指左其中1個狼人朋友係狼人 其他人都信佢 所以其中1個狼人朋友<br />\n就比人白天投死<br />\n第3晚 我本身想殺預言家 但另1個狼人朋友指左另1個人 (後尾完左先知係女巫) 佢竟然守衛到佢<br />\n<br />\n呢個位大家係咪已經覺得唔對路 ?<br />\n<br />\n首先個位朋友係無跳女巫身份 但佢偏偏唔守衛明跳既預言家<br />\n而走去救1個我地唔知既女巫 ? 我個時己經r哂頭 心諗有冇咁準呀<br />\n<br />\n第4日我同佢已經係無寧兩可既狀態 好似殺咩都比人守衛到咁 最後預言家跳埋出黎話見到我<br />\n係狼 而個位守衛就游說女巫毒死個狼人朋友 而佢所謂既&quot;理由&quot;係佢既直覺覺得佢係狼人<br />\n最後女巫又真係信左佢講野 最後我同朋友一齊死 end game 我已經好無奈<br />\n<br />\n第2鋪 佢係平民<br />\n<br />\n到佢發言個時用佢所謂既&quot;理由&quot; 話聽到右面有聲同又用佢既&quot;直覺&quot;覺得佢係狼人<br />\n就話咩我覺得你係狼人喎 又同預言家女巫個d人講 我信你地多d去煽動班好人聽佢講 <br />\n總之最後都係估啱哂所有狼人<br />\n<br />\n第3鋪 佢係狼人<br />\n<br />\n第1晚 佢就就殺啱左預言家<br />\n第2晚 佢就殺左女巫 女巫無得自救<br />\n其他唔講總之就好快解決哂d神職<br />\n<br />\n所以到最後我想講既係 我完全諗唔明一班朋友點解要玩隻game都要偷睇作弊 ?<br />\n咁樣玩落去有咩意思 ? 因為咁贏左又有咩咁值得高興 ?<br />\n我地平時玩大約有8-10個人 而家圍威喂班朋友計埋我有4個知佢係出貓<br />\n其他人我唔知佢地知唔知佢出貓定係唔出聲扮唔知 我真係唔知<br />\n<br />\n而家班活動有佢係度我地就唔會主張玩狼人 就算佢話想玩 我同班fd都會話唔玩<br />\n玩d佢唔會出到貓既board game<br />\n<br />\n真係好無癮 因為一個人搞到要轉game 所以唔知各位巴絲有冇遇過類似問題<br />\n唔想為左隻game搞到同佢反面 可唔可以教下小弟點解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 平時少開post 講得1999 唔好意思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我知你地班朋友有上開連登 勿相認唔該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a48c8cbcb568e2e7c6fbcc9a08c266a4d08b8c","tid":868053,"uid":46611,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"玩一夜狼人好過啦"},{"pid":"a6670a27b8f6af7a01f0171c8fbf4282b52f0875","tid":868053,"uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"03a48c8cbcb568e2e7c6fbcc9a08c266a4d08b8c","tid":868053,"uid":46611,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"玩一夜狼人好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"呢個有試過 有搗蛋鬼同強盜調亂哂d牌<br />\n佢偷睇都無用 但我地都係鐘意玩正常狼人多d"},{"pid":"c97fee45838c124be8353bbeda8686a6557847ea","tid":868053,"uid":208977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:06:27.000Z","msg":"冇人做主持咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748f51e095c2ecff744f6f6ad10b17aedefa3f8b","tid":868053,"uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97fee45838c124be8353bbeda8686a6557847ea","tid":868053,"uid":208977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:06:27.000Z","msg":"冇人做主持咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:12:51.000Z","msg":"有人做主持 但個個朋友唔係好熟 所以我地無問到佢"},{"pid":"0aad08562f39f6530f2087924d489f11978b30d8","tid":868053,"uid":9726,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01ef34be567d14a681ac339f378a8f7448326df0","tid":868053,"uid":19867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"一巴車落佢到"},{"pid":"7afba510923dab1ba2d8be67d8ce1ddd3e1cb6bb","tid":868053,"uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aad08562f39f6530f2087924d489f11978b30d8","tid":868053,"uid":9726,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"我都想 但呢一班人一早識左好耐 好難排除佢<br />\n無佢係度一班人一定首選玩狼人先<br />\n有佢係度就局住玩其他game <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d44070937ef8c6c13dfcb778d84da306151f1a","tid":868053,"uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"01ef34be567d14a681ac339f378a8f7448326df0","tid":868053,"uid":19867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"一巴車落佢到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"會反面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c6c95647744a085e402334e61b448452d7c531","tid":868053,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"趁佢偷望果陣同佢四目交投"},{"pid":"220e5c1d8511d8d6f880aa5be2a67e5a21246cd1","tid":868053,"uid":189269,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"玩呢啲game都出貓有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偷睇扮自己估到威啲？"},{"pid":"96de4a220bf65d78ca2e2e9e19c87357aeb60770","tid":868053,"uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3c6c95647744a085e402334e61b448452d7c531","tid":868053,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"趁佢偷望果陣同佢四目交投"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"我fd咁係咁 我之前所謂夜晚睇到佢偷睇<br />\n因為個時我fd坐正係出貓個條友對面<br />\n我fd望完佢出貓之後到天黑佢先成個人&quot;烏&quot;低身同用雙手遮住自己咁避開嫌疑<br />\n其實佢咁做先暗示佢之前係偷睇<br />\n係fd後尾同我講返 因為我個時坐係偷睇條友隔離同埋玩緊唔知<br />\n其實唔止呢3鋪 就算佢比人發現左 第2日玩佢都係偷睇 (冇烏低身)"},{"pid":"7ecd6732b504f65bfa7d3654db12e666969f1297","tid":868053,"uid":57555,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"咁唔直接問佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁玩大家都冇癮啦"},{"pid":"c5f9f8dd157a334532df42e0475a1391784ac24a","tid":868053,"uid":110309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:35:31.000Z","msg":"直接攤牌問佢係咪偷睇<br />\n<br />\n明知佢偷睇仲繼續同佢一齊玩真係浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c33c1254fc6c83e618f568471c6f854c14ad23e","tid":868053,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47b811ca09c0b88421ff71280e01bab200efd725","tid":868053,"uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"220e5c1d8511d8d6f880aa5be2a67e5a21246cd1","tid":868053,"uid":189269,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"玩呢啲game都出貓有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偷睇扮自己估到威啲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:38:22.000Z","msg":"唉 所以我就係唔明 可能佢以為咁做d朋友會以為佢好醒同好叻 <br />\n佢會好自豪"},{"pid":"be64ec23651ae699455200524c4ba003aba2f838","tid":868053,"uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ecd6732b504f65bfa7d3654db12e666969f1297","tid":868053,"uid":57555,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"咁唔直接問佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁玩大家都冇癮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"直接問佢佢肯定會否認同埋一定會反面<br />\n我地就係唔想為左隻game同佢反面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22432b66f024751f5544da185594b76cf2bc2799","tid":868053,"uid":148635,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c5f9f8dd157a334532df42e0475a1391784ac24a","tid":868053,"uid":110309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:35:31.000Z","msg":"直接攤牌問佢係咪偷睇<br />\n<br />\n明知佢偷睇仲繼續同佢一齊玩真係浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"唔得 佢一定會否認同埋反面 <br />\n我地就係唔想為左隻game反面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n矛盾點就係呢度 大家都想玩狼人 大家都知佢出貓 咁點 <br />\n為左隻game無左個朋友 值得咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172e1acb854aec57e5c714ef5737009